{
  "stem": "11998.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my father and I, we ran over to the group where he was lining them up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He shoved me in between two men on either side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he kept on doing whatever he was doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was very unusual because, firstly, most of the times, the soldiers-- I mean, the-- the prisoners from the camp were coming to the-- to meet the trains.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were lining up the people in rows of five and marching them out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some soldiers that were doing-- I mean, some striped uniform prisoners, they were doing that anyways.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So for him to ask my father was unusual.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he was doing that, one of the Nazi soldiers came by.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he looked at my father, and he recognized him from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he tried to make contact, and he tried to figure out where he knew him from.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By that time, nobody wore the-- the Star of David, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so he started a conversation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father spoke fluent German, so they tried to figure out whether he's a neighbor of his from Chorzow, or whether he met him at the factory, the diesel factory.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At any rate, he-- my father grabbed the opportunity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, my son is in the other lineup, and I would like to have him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he-- he agreed to have me-- let me have.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that line up that I was in, you know, a few minutes later, was marched off to the-- to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the meantime, while I was still standing there, the womens were being loaded onto the trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I saw a girlfriend of mine that lived in the same apartment that we lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we waved to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
